{"tid":133553,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"尖沙咀提款被「食卡」 大陸仔徒手拆毀ATM機","createTime":"2017-02-24T16:37:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-26T07:48:05.000Z","uid":122,"like":84,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9a12a0c7c235768ee6deabbd285ff66150b950e8","tid":133553,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T16:37:38.000Z","msg":"<strong>提款被「食卡」 內地狂男徒手拆毀ATM機</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170224/large/1487948155_4cd0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170224%2Flarge%2F1487948155_4cd0.jpg&h=dd30ac22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n晚上近9時，一名內地男於尖沙嘴碼頭附近的滙豐銀行ATM自動櫃員機提款，惟其間不知何故被「食卡」，內地男隨即怒火中燒，不停搖晃該部櫃員機，有途人見狀報警。警員到場調查，見櫃員機的頂部已被扯出拆毀，更露出內裏銀行的交易收據，遂即場拘捕28歲姓廖的內地男子。"},{"pid":"61d0127732991c10dc9091cdda406558d63d5a44","tid":133553,"uid":46309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T16:38:20.000Z","msg":"痴撚線"},{"pid":"dd07b805dded5a3fc729a5dc4e07238d4def00ec","tid":133553,"uid":42550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T16:40:25.000Z","msg":"摩登如來神掌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ec67ed9becb37d1b85755317d0ca75eee234c1c","tid":133553,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T16:41:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><strong>提款被「食卡」 內地狂男徒手拆毀ATM機</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170224/large/1487948155_4cd0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170224%2Flarge%2F1487948155_4cd0.jpg&h=dd30ac22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n晚上近9時，一名內地男於尖沙嘴碼頭附近的滙豐銀行ATM自動櫃員機提款，惟其間不知何故被「食卡」，內地男隨即怒火中燒，不停搖晃該部櫃員機，有途人見狀報警。警員到場調查，見櫃員機的頂部已被扯出拆毀，更露出內裏銀行的交易收據，遂即場拘捕28歲姓廖的內地男子。</blockquote><br />\n食卡係人都嬲嘅<br />\n但駛唔駛咁"},{"pid":"94953